I wish I had someone to talk to. I recently had really bad anxiety last night. When I do spiral I text my bf and he ends up worrying for me. I didn't text him the rest of the day because I was trying to recollect myself and I know he's busy working. 

He later texted me that he was worried the whole day. I called him to let him know I was doing better and let him know what happened. 

Now I feel guilty for worrying him and he said his head hurt and he's going to sleep. Maybe he won't say anything but I feel like I worried him for nothing. Now I feel like I should stop texting him for a few days because I honestly feel like a burden. 

I can't keep it all to myself. I end up going to a dark place and feel alone. I self-harmed one time a from anxiety and guilt that snowballed. I feel those thoughts creeping up and I really don't want it to lead to that. 

I also just have a hard time opening up to friends. Mostly because I feel like there needs a place and time. I'm getting better at opening up more and more but it takes time and mental health discussions are something that I haven't worked towards yet. It's probably the hardest obstacle for me.

There's no way I can afford any therapy to help with these habits right now. I don't have a summer job and I'm going to college in the fall so I may have to save some money or something.

I suppose I can try counseling again at the university. I just hate that it takes a while to get an appointment. Thank you for anyone who's finished reading this.'

'I know I should die for the good of a lot of people. But I am a coward who could not take a few seconds of pain. As always I remain a living fat bastard unworthy of anything. Here I am yet again the same loser who would never make it out of this treacherous pit. I've been trying to push myself to kill myself for the last few weeks. Tgere were moments of ups and downs. But I just cant. I chicken out like I did in almost everything in life. 

I'm almost 30 years old for fuck sake. I don't have a job coz I am so stressed to work in the fucking accounting and auditing field I have knowledge about. I am "trying" to get a job for the sake of my grandma eho us worried sick of me. My parents are still trusting my sorry ass that I would find a job and get martied snd "live happily ever after". How can I tell them that I have let them down?

 The rest of my family have lost hope in me. I have had warnings and serious advices from all family members to get my act straight. I've been called a laxy bum by my relatives. My brother calls me a selfish guy as I am living on other people's money and almost disowned me. I know he didn't and I wish he did. 

I don't mean to sit on my ass and play township all day eating sleeping and shitting forever. I wish I could be on my own. But the thought of life scares me. I hate the field I'm semi qualified for. I fucked up the final exams after wasting an year including the lockdown and postponement of exams last year. I tried to find a way out of this field but all my "unrealistic" ideas didn't seem to work. I thought I could become a part time teacher as I always liked to teach. But my brother who is a very successful and know it all genius of the family pointed out that teachers are already jobless and I am a stupid idiot who would fail his students as he can't even get himself to pass an exam. I can't become a writer coz that requires some intelligence which I don't have. I can't run a business of my own as I am broke and I would fail that too. I can't do anything else. I am stuck and keep going down this quicksand pit. 

Even if I suck it up and get a job in the audit field, what am I gonna do? I would be replaced by someon who is actually resourceful in a matter of no time. Even if I become good in my job, what next? Work for 60 hours a week for the next 30 years on something that drives me crazy? Get married for the sake of family? Get a bunch of kids snd add their well being and education into the list of my ever expanding troubles? Make connections with people I don't like for the sake of social status? Why is that life for anyway? 

What the fuck is wrong with me? Everyone else seems to be enjoying this godforsaken way of life that has sslaved us to our luxuries and  social status. Why can't I suck it up and become a zombie and do whatever I'm told to? Why is my brain not able to get the message? 

I have been noticed by teachers and friends to have signs of ADHD sibce school days. But my family who don't believe in mental illness knows better. They know that I'm a lazy awkward idiot who didn't learn to focus his thoughts and is still immature and can't handle being a MAN as my brother is. 

I know there's a million quotes about "we can live the life we want and nobody can stop us" or "Work hard and be successful" shit. But whst is the point in all of that if I ultimately despise the fucking life itself?

What is the point to anything? Am I in hell? Is this the way I get tortured for eternity? I got molested by my aunt's sister when I was 7 and my  brother when I was 8. Both of them were also underage during that time. So they dropped their load on me. At least I didn't molest anyone to satisfy my curiosity. I just learned masturbation when I was 10 and did it like 4 times a day until I turned 25. I developed a craving for pleasure even before I knew what it is. I am still suffering fighting hard to control my thoughts. 

I dropped out of school when I was 13 and put back in school at 19. Worked my way through without thinking about what I really want and went on with what my family thought would be good for my future. Well that's what you get being born in a dysfunctional family and having mental illness. I am suffering from depression and anxiety for the last 6 years. Well everyone else thinks that I'm lazy and moody. Maybe that is what i am. 

I am a useless piece of garbage. No even garbage can be recycled or turned into manure or something. I am just a waste of a life being a burden on everyone adding carbon dioxide to the earth. 

I have tried several times to take myself out the last few weeks. Hanging myself, drowning myself, falling from the 3rd floor on to the road below, hanging again. But. i just can't go through it. I can't live, I can't die. Story of my life is nothing but waste of time and resources. 

I wish I could just go through it. A few seconds of pain is enough. I would dir and the world would be a better place.

For fuck sake give me a heart attack or something. Haven't I had enough? What more fucked up shit is shead for me?

Hindu mythology says hell is filled with torture methods like boiling pas of oil and fire to torture the bad people. I used to believe that. But now I understand hell is life. Hell is what I am in right now. My own mind that is tormenting me and giving me hope so that it can torment me more.
